quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  109,1,"Say: \"You, you the disbelievers"
  109,2,I do not worship what you worship
  109,3,And you are not worshipping what I worship
  109,4,And nor I am worshipping what you worshipped
  109,5,And nor you are worshipping what I worship
  109,6,"For you (is) your religion, and for me (is) my religion"